extendedInfo.description: MissionTo bring forth a God-filled anointed word in a very unique, common sense way to where all can receive and eat. We promise to never be so spiritually high to where we are no earthly good.Company OverviewSunday Morning Breakfast is a Tellius Carr Production bringing the world God's Word, from the pulpit to the streets. "Man does not live on bread alone, but on every word that comes from the mouth of God." --- Matthew 4:4 (NIV) We feed our audience primarily through radio and written word, but also through visual art, music, and charitable work.DescriptionThe Sunday Morning Breakfast Radio Show is ALL Real Talk ... All the Time ... On-Time ... Through God's Word. Come As You Are & We Will Satisfy Your Spiritual Hunger.
